history.created_by: /bin/sh -c #(nop)  LABEL org.label-schema.schema-version=1.0 org.label-schema.name=CentOS Base Image org.label-schema.vendor=CentOS org.label-schema.license=GPLv2 org.label-schema.build-date=20200809 org.opencontainers.image.title=CentOS Base Image org.opencontainers.image.vendor=CentOS org.opencontainers.image.licenses=GPL-2.0-only org.opencontainers.image.created=2020-08-09 00:00:00+01:00

/bin/sh -c #(nop) ENV SUMMARY="Base image which allows using of source-to-image."	    DESCRIPTION="The s2i-core image provides any images layered on top of it with all the tools needed to use source-to-image functionality while keeping the image size as small as possible."

/bin/sh -c #(nop) LABEL summary="$SUMMARY"       description="$DESCRIPTION"       io.k8s.description="$DESCRIPTION"       io.k8s.display-name="s2i core"       io.openshift.s2i.scripts-url=image:///usr/libexec/s2i       io.s2i.scripts-url=image:///usr/libexec/s2i       com.redhat.component="s2i-core-container"       name="centos7/s2i-core-centos7"       version="1"       maintainer="SoftwareCollections.org <sclorg@redhat.com>"

/bin/sh -c #(nop) ENV     STI_SCRIPTS_URL=image:///usr/libexec/s2i     STI_SCRIPTS_PATH=/usr/libexec/s2i     APP_ROOT=/opt/app-root     HOME=/opt/app-root/src     PATH=/opt/app-root/src/bin:/opt/app-root/bin:$PATH     PLATFORM="el7"

/bin/sh -c rpmkeys --import file:///etc/pki/rpm-gpg/RPM-GPG-KEY-CentOS-7 &&   INSTALL_PKGS="bsdtar   findutils   gettext   groff-base   rsync   scl-utils   tar   unzip   yum-utils" &&   mkdir -p ${HOME}/.pki/nssdb &&   chown -R 1001:0 ${HOME}/.pki &&   yum install -y --setopt=tsflags=nodocs $INSTALL_PKGS &&   rpm -V $INSTALL_PKGS &&   yum -y clean all --enablerepo='*'
/bin/sh -c rpm-file-permissions &&   useradd -u 1001 -r -g 0 -d ${HOME} -s /sbin/nologin       -c "Default Application User" default &&   chown -R 1001:0 ${APP_ROOT}

/bin/sh -c #(nop) ENV SUMMARY="Base image which allows using of source-to-image."	    DESCRIPTION="The s2i-core image provides any images layered on top of it with all the tools needed to use source-to-image functionality while keeping the image size as small as possible."

/bin/sh -c #(nop) LABEL summary="$SUMMARY"       description="$DESCRIPTION"       io.k8s.description="$DESCRIPTION"       io.k8s.display-name="s2i core"       io.openshift.s2i.scripts-url=image:///usr/libexec/s2i       io.s2i.scripts-url=image:///usr/libexec/s2i       com.redhat.component="s2i-core-container"       name="centos7/s2i-core-centos7"       version="1"       maintainer="SoftwareCollections.org <sclorg@redhat.com>"

/bin/sh -c #(nop) ENV     STI_SCRIPTS_URL=image:///usr/libexec/s2i     STI_SCRIPTS_PATH=/usr/libexec/s2i     APP_ROOT=/opt/app-root     HOME=/opt/app-root/src     PATH=/opt/app-root/src/bin:/opt/app-root/bin:$PATH     PLATFORM="el7"

/bin/sh -c rpmkeys --import file:///etc/pki/rpm-gpg/RPM-GPG-KEY-CentOS-7 &&   INSTALL_PKGS="bsdtar   findutils   gettext   groff-base   rsync   scl-utils   tar   unzip   yum-utils" &&   mkdir -p ${HOME}/.pki/nssdb &&   chown -R 1001:0 ${HOME}/.pki &&   yum install -y --setopt=tsflags=nodocs $INSTALL_PKGS &&   rpm -V $INSTALL_PKGS &&   yum -y clean all --enablerepo='*'
/bin/sh -c rpm-file-permissions &&   useradd -u 1001 -r -g 0 -d ${HOME} -s /sbin/nologin       -c "Default Application User" default &&   chown -R 1001:0 ${APP_ROOT}

history.created_by: /bin/sh -c #(nop)  LABEL org.label-schema.schema-version=1.0 org.label-schema.name=CentOS Base Image org.label-schema.vendor=CentOS org.label-schema.license=GPLv2 org.label-schema.build-date=20200809 org.opencontainers.image.title=CentOS Base Image org.opencontainers.image.vendor=CentOS org.opencontainers.image.licenses=GPL-2.0-only org.opencontainers.image.created=2020-08-09 00:00:00+01:00

/bin/sh -c #(nop) ENV SUMMARY="Base image which allows using of source-to-image."	    DESCRIPTION="The s2i-core image provides any images layered on top of it with all the tools needed to use source-to-image functionality while keeping the image size as small as possible."

/bin/sh -c #(nop) LABEL summary="$SUMMARY"       description="$DESCRIPTION"       io.k8s.description="$DESCRIPTION"       io.k8s.display-name="s2i core"       io.openshift.s2i.scripts-url=image:///usr/libexec/s2i       io.s2i.scripts-url=image:///usr/libexec/s2i       com.redhat.component="s2i-core-container"       name="centos7/s2i-core-centos7"       version="1"       maintainer="SoftwareCollections.org <sclorg@redhat.com>"

/bin/sh -c #(nop) ENV     STI_SCRIPTS_URL=image:///usr/libexec/s2i     STI_SCRIPTS_PATH=/usr/libexec/s2i     APP_ROOT=/opt/app-root     HOME=/opt/app-root/src     PATH=/opt/app-root/src/bin:/opt/app-root/bin:$PATH     PLATFORM="el7"

/bin/sh -c rpmkeys --import file:///etc/pki/rpm-gpg/RPM-GPG-KEY-CentOS-7 &&   INSTALL_PKGS="bsdtar   findutils   gettext   groff-base   rsync   scl-utils   tar   unzip   yum-utils" &&   mkdir -p ${HOME}/.pki/nssdb &&   chown -R 1001:0 ${HOME}/.pki &&   yum install -y --setopt=tsflags=nodocs $INSTALL_PKGS &&   rpm -V $INSTALL_PKGS &&   yum -y clean all --enablerepo='*'
/bin/sh -c rpm-file-permissions &&   useradd -u 1001 -r -g 0 -d ${HOME} -s /sbin/nologin       -c "Default Application User" default &&   chown -R 1001:0 ${APP_ROOT}

history.created_by: /bin/sh -c #(nop)  LABEL org.label-schema.schema-version=1.0 org.label-schema.name=CentOS Base Image org.label-schema.vendor=CentOS org.label-schema.license=GPLv2 org.label-schema.build-date=20200809 org.opencontainers.image.title=CentOS Base Image org.opencontainers.image.vendor=CentOS org.opencontainers.image.licenses=GPL-2.0-only org.opencontainers.image.created=2020-08-09 00:00:00+01:00

/bin/sh -c #(nop) ENV SUMMARY="Base image which allows using of source-to-image."	    DESCRIPTION="The s2i-core image provides any images layered on top of it with all the tools needed to use source-to-image functionality while keeping the image size as small as possible."

/bin/sh -c #(nop) LABEL summary="$SUMMARY"       description="$DESCRIPTION"       io.k8s.description="$DESCRIPTION"       io.k8s.display-name="s2i core"       io.openshift.s2i.scripts-url=image:///usr/libexec/s2i       io.s2i.scripts-url=image:///usr/libexec/s2i       com.redhat.component="s2i-core-container"       name="centos7/s2i-core-centos7"       version="1"       maintainer="SoftwareCollections.org <sclorg@redhat.com>"

/bin/sh -c #(nop) ENV     STI_SCRIPTS_URL=image:///usr/libexec/s2i     STI_SCRIPTS_PATH=/usr/libexec/s2i     APP_ROOT=/opt/app-root     HOME=/opt/app-root/src     PATH=/opt/app-root/src/bin:/opt/app-root/bin:$PATH     PLATFORM="el7"

/bin/sh -c rpmkeys --import file:///etc/pki/rpm-gpg/RPM-GPG-KEY-CentOS-7 &&   INSTALL_PKGS="bsdtar   findutils   gettext   groff-base   rsync   scl-utils   tar   unzip   yum-utils" &&   mkdir -p ${HOME}/.pki/nssdb &&   chown -R 1001:0 ${HOME}/.pki &&   yum install -y --setopt=tsflags=nodocs $INSTALL_PKGS &&   rpm -V $INSTALL_PKGS &&   yum -y clean all --enablerepo='*'
/bin/sh -c rpm-file-permissions &&   useradd -u 1001 -r -g 0 -d ${HOME} -s /sbin/nologin       -c "Default Application User" default &&   chown -R 1001:0 ${APP_ROOT}

Labels.description: The s2i-core image provides any images layered on top of it with all the tools needed to use source-to-image functionality while keeping the image size as small as possible.
Labels.io.k8s.description: The s2i-core image provides any images layered on top of it with all the tools needed to use source-to-image functionality while keeping the image size as small as possible.
Labels.name: centos7/s2i-core-centos7
Labels.org.label-schema.name: CentOS Base Image
Labels.org.opencontainers.image.title: CentOS Base Image
Labels.summary: Base image which allows using of source-to-image.

history.created_by: /bin/sh -c #(nop)  LABEL org.label-schema.schema-version=1.0 org.label-schema.name=CentOS Base Image org.label-schema.vendor=CentOS org.label-schema.license=GPLv2 org.label-schema.build-date=20200809 org.opencontainers.image.title=CentOS Base Image org.opencontainers.image.vendor=CentOS org.opencontainers.image.licenses=GPL-2.0-only org.opencontainers.image.created=2020-08-09 00:00:00+01:00

/bin/sh -c #(nop) ENV SUMMARY="Base image which allows using of source-to-image."	    DESCRIPTION="The s2i-core image provides any images layered on top of it with all the tools needed to use source-to-image functionality while keeping the image size as small as possible."

/bin/sh -c #(nop) LABEL summary="$SUMMARY"       description="$DESCRIPTION"       io.k8s.description="$DESCRIPTION"       io.k8s.display-name="s2i core"       io.openshift.s2i.scripts-url=image:///usr/libexec/s2i       io.s2i.scripts-url=image:///usr/libexec/s2i       com.redhat.component="s2i-core-container"       name="centos7/s2i-core-centos7"       version="1"       maintainer="SoftwareCollections.org <sclorg@redhat.com>"

/bin/sh -c #(nop) ENV     STI_SCRIPTS_URL=image:///usr/libexec/s2i     STI_SCRIPTS_PATH=/usr/libexec/s2i     APP_ROOT=/opt/app-root     HOME=/opt/app-root/src     PATH=/opt/app-root/src/bin:/opt/app-root/bin:$PATH     PLATFORM="el7"

/bin/sh -c rpmkeys --import file:///etc/pki/rpm-gpg/RPM-GPG-KEY-CentOS-7 &&   INSTALL_PKGS="bsdtar   findutils   gettext   groff-base   rsync   scl-utils   tar   unzip   yum-utils" &&   mkdir -p ${HOME}/.pki/nssdb &&   chown -R 1001:0 ${HOME}/.pki &&   yum install -y --setopt=tsflags=nodocs $INSTALL_PKGS &&   rpm -V $INSTALL_PKGS &&   yum -y clean all --enablerepo='*'
/bin/sh -c rpm-file-permissions &&   useradd -u 1001 -r -g 0 -d ${HOME} -s /sbin/nologin       -c "Default Application User" default &&   chown -R 1001:0 ${APP_ROOT}

/bin/sh -c #(nop) LABEL summary="$SUMMARY"       description="$DESCRIPTION"       io.k8s.description="$DESCRIPTION"       io.k8s.display-name="s2i core"       io.openshift.s2i.scripts-url=image:///usr/libexec/s2i       io.s2i.scripts-url=image:///usr/libexec/s2i       com.redhat.component="s2i-core-container"       name="centos7/s2i-core-centos7"       version="1"       maintainer="SoftwareCollections.org <sclorg@redhat.com>"

/bin/sh -c #(nop) ENV     STI_SCRIPTS_URL=image:///usr/libexec/s2i     STI_SCRIPTS_PATH=/usr/libexec/s2i     APP_ROOT=/opt/app-root     HOME=/opt/app-root/src     PATH=/opt/app-root/src/bin:/opt/app-root/bin:$PATH     PLATFORM="el7"

history.created_by: /bin/sh -c #(nop)  LABEL org.label-schema.schema-version=1.0 org.label-schema.name=CentOS Base Image org.label-schema.vendor=CentOS org.label-schema.license=GPLv2 org.label-schema.build-date=20200809 org.opencontainers.image.title=CentOS Base Image org.opencontainers.image.vendor=CentOS org.opencontainers.image.licenses=GPL-2.0-only org.opencontainers.image.created=2020-08-09 00:00:00+01:00

/bin/sh -c #(nop) ENV SUMMARY="Base image which allows using of source-to-image."	    DESCRIPTION="The s2i-core image provides any images layered on top of it with all the tools needed to use source-to-image functionality while keeping the image size as small as possible."

/bin/sh -c #(nop) LABEL summary="$SUMMARY"       description="$DESCRIPTION"       io.k8s.description="$DESCRIPTION"       io.k8s.display-name="s2i core"       io.openshift.s2i.scripts-url=image:///usr/libexec/s2i       io.s2i.scripts-url=image:///usr/libexec/s2i       com.redhat.component="s2i-core-container"       name="centos7/s2i-core-centos7"       version="1"       maintainer="SoftwareCollections.org <sclorg@redhat.com>"

/bin/sh -c #(nop) ENV     STI_SCRIPTS_URL=image:///usr/libexec/s2i     STI_SCRIPTS_PATH=/usr/libexec/s2i     APP_ROOT=/opt/app-root     HOME=/opt/app-root/src     PATH=/opt/app-root/src/bin:/opt/app-root/bin:$PATH     PLATFORM="el7"

/bin/sh -c rpmkeys --import file:///etc/pki/rpm-gpg/RPM-GPG-KEY-CentOS-7 &&   INSTALL_PKGS="bsdtar   findutils   gettext   groff-base   rsync   scl-utils   tar   unzip   yum-utils" &&   mkdir -p ${HOME}/.pki/nssdb &&   chown -R 1001:0 ${HOME}/.pki &&   yum install -y --setopt=tsflags=nodocs $INSTALL_PKGS &&   rpm -V $INSTALL_PKGS &&   yum -y clean all --enablerepo='*'
/bin/sh -c rpm-file-permissions &&   useradd -u 1001 -r -g 0 -d ${HOME} -s /sbin/nologin       -c "Default Application User" default &&   chown -R 1001:0 ${APP_ROOT}

/bin/sh -c #(nop) LABEL summary="$SUMMARY"       description="$DESCRIPTION"       io.k8s.description="$DESCRIPTION"       io.k8s.display-name="s2i core"       io.openshift.s2i.scripts-url=image:///usr/libexec/s2i       io.s2i.scripts-url=image:///usr/libexec/s2i       com.redhat.component="s2i-core-container"       name="centos7/s2i-core-centos7"       version="1"       maintainer="SoftwareCollections.org <sclorg@redhat.com>"

/bin/sh -c #(nop) ENV     STI_SCRIPTS_URL=image:///usr/libexec/s2i     STI_SCRIPTS_PATH=/usr/libexec/s2i     APP_ROOT=/opt/app-root     HOME=/opt/app-root/src     PATH=/opt/app-root/src/bin:/opt/app-root/bin:$PATH     PLATFORM="el7"

/bin/sh -c rpmkeys --import file:///etc/pki/rpm-gpg/RPM-GPG-KEY-CentOS-7 &&   INSTALL_PKGS="bsdtar   findutils   gettext   groff-base   rsync   scl-utils   tar   unzip   yum-utils" &&   mkdir -p ${HOME}/.pki/nssdb &&   chown -R 1001:0 ${HOME}/.pki &&   yum install -y --setopt=tsflags=nodocs $INSTALL_PKGS &&   rpm -V $INSTALL_PKGS &&   yum -y clean all --enablerepo='*'
/bin/sh -c rpm-file-permissions &&   useradd -u 1001 -r -g 0 -d ${HOME} -s /sbin/nologin       -c "Default Application User" default &&   chown -R 1001:0 ${APP_ROOT}

/bin/sh -c #(nop) LABEL summary="$SUMMARY"       description="$DESCRIPTION"       io.k8s.description="$DESCRIPTION"       io.k8s.display-name="s2i core"       io.openshift.s2i.scripts-url=image:///usr/libexec/s2i       io.s2i.scripts-url=image:///usr/libexec/s2i       com.redhat.component="s2i-core-container"       name="centos7/s2i-core-centos7"       version="1"       maintainer="SoftwareCollections.org <sclorg@redhat.com>"

/bin/sh -c #(nop) ENV     STI_SCRIPTS_URL=image:///usr/libexec/s2i     STI_SCRIPTS_PATH=/usr/libexec/s2i     APP_ROOT=/opt/app-root     HOME=/opt/app-root/src     PATH=/opt/app-root/src/bin:/opt/app-root/bin:$PATH     PLATFORM="el7"

/bin/sh -c rpmkeys --import file:///etc/pki/rpm-gpg/RPM-GPG-KEY-CentOS-7 &&   INSTALL_PKGS="bsdtar   findutils   gettext   groff-base   rsync   scl-utils   tar   unzip   yum-utils" &&   mkdir -p ${HOME}/.pki/nssdb &&   chown -R 1001:0 ${HOME}/.pki &&   yum install -y --setopt=tsflags=nodocs $INSTALL_PKGS &&   rpm -V $INSTALL_PKGS &&   yum -y clean all --enablerepo='*'
/bin/sh -c rpm-file-permissions &&   useradd -u 1001 -r -g 0 -d ${HOME} -s /sbin/nologin       -c "Default Application User" default &&   chown -R 1001:0 ${APP_ROOT}

/bin/sh -c #(nop) LABEL summary="$SUMMARY"       description="$DESCRIPTION"       io.k8s.description="$DESCRIPTION"       io.k8s.display-name="s2i core"       io.openshift.s2i.scripts-url=image:///usr/libexec/s2i       io.s2i.scripts-url=image:///usr/libexec/s2i       com.redhat.component="s2i-core-container"       name="centos7/s2i-core-centos7"       version="1"       maintainer="SoftwareCollections.org <sclorg@redhat.com>"

/bin/sh -c #(nop) ENV     STI_SCRIPTS_URL=image:///usr/libexec/s2i     STI_SCRIPTS_PATH=/usr/libexec/s2i     APP_ROOT=/opt/app-root     HOME=/opt/app-root/src     PATH=/opt/app-root/src/bin:/opt/app-root/bin:$PATH     PLATFORM="el7"

/bin/sh -c rpmkeys --import file:///etc/pki/rpm-gpg/RPM-GPG-KEY-CentOS-7 &&   INSTALL_PKGS="bsdtar   findutils   gettext   groff-base   rsync   scl-utils   tar   unzip   yum-utils" &&   mkdir -p ${HOME}/.pki/nssdb &&   chown -R 1001:0 ${HOME}/.pki &&   yum install -y --setopt=tsflags=nodocs $INSTALL_PKGS &&   rpm -V $INSTALL_PKGS &&   yum -y clean all --enablerepo='*'
/bin/sh -c rpm-file-permissions &&   useradd -u 1001 -r -g 0 -d ${HOME} -s /sbin/nologin       -c "Default Application User" default &&   chown -R 1001:0 ${APP_ROOT}

/bin/sh -c #(nop) LABEL summary="$SUMMARY"       description="$DESCRIPTION"       io.k8s.description="$DESCRIPTION"       io.k8s.display-name="s2i core"       io.openshift.s2i.scripts-url=image:///usr/libexec/s2i       io.s2i.scripts-url=image:///usr/libexec/s2i       com.redhat.component="s2i-core-container"       name="centos7/s2i-core-centos7"       version="1"       maintainer="SoftwareCollections.org <sclorg@redhat.com>"

/bin/sh -c #(nop) ENV     STI_SCRIPTS_URL=image:///usr/libexec/s2i     STI_SCRIPTS_PATH=/usr/libexec/s2i     APP_ROOT=/opt/app-root     HOME=/opt/app-root/src     PATH=/opt/app-root/src/bin:/opt/app-root/bin:$PATH     PLATFORM="el7"

/bin/sh -c rpmkeys --import file:///etc/pki/rpm-gpg/RPM-GPG-KEY-CentOS-7 &&   INSTALL_PKGS="bsdtar   findutils   gettext   groff-base   rsync   scl-utils   tar   unzip   yum-utils" &&   mkdir -p ${HOME}/.pki/nssdb &&   chown -R 1001:0 ${HOME}/.pki &&   yum install -y --setopt=tsflags=nodocs $INSTALL_PKGS &&   rpm -V $INSTALL_PKGS &&   yum -y clean all --enablerepo='*'
/bin/sh -c rpm-file-permissions &&   useradd -u 1001 -r -g 0 -d ${HOME} -s /sbin/nologin       -c "Default Application User" default &&   chown -R 1001:0 ${APP_ROOT}

/bin/sh -c #(nop) LABEL summary="$SUMMARY"       description="$DESCRIPTION"       io.k8s.description="$DESCRIPTION"       io.k8s.display-name="s2i core"       io.openshift.s2i.scripts-url=image:///usr/libexec/s2i       io.s2i.scripts-url=image:///usr/libexec/s2i       com.redhat.component="s2i-core-container"       name="centos7/s2i-core-centos7"       version="1"       maintainer="SoftwareCollections.org <sclorg@redhat.com>"

/bin/sh -c #(nop) ENV     STI_SCRIPTS_URL=image:///usr/libexec/s2i     STI_SCRIPTS_PATH=/usr/libexec/s2i     APP_ROOT=/opt/app-root     HOME=/opt/app-root/src     PATH=/opt/app-root/src/bin:/opt/app-root/bin:$PATH     PLATFORM="el7"

/bin/sh -c rpmkeys --import file:///etc/pki/rpm-gpg/RPM-GPG-KEY-CentOS-7 &&   INSTALL_PKGS="bsdtar   findutils   gettext   groff-base   rsync   scl-utils   tar   unzip   yum-utils" &&   mkdir -p ${HOME}/.pki/nssdb &&   chown -R 1001:0 ${HOME}/.pki &&   yum install -y --setopt=tsflags=nodocs $INSTALL_PKGS &&   rpm -V $INSTALL_PKGS &&   yum -y clean all --enablerepo='*'
/bin/sh -c rpm-file-permissions &&   useradd -u 1001 -r -g 0 -d ${HOME} -s /sbin/nologin       -c "Default Application User" default &&   chown -R 1001:0 ${APP_ROOT}

/bin/sh -c #(nop) LABEL summary="$SUMMARY"       description="$DESCRIPTION"       io.k8s.description="$DESCRIPTION"       io.k8s.display-name="s2i core"       io.openshift.s2i.scripts-url=image:///usr/libexec/s2i       io.s2i.scripts-url=image:///usr/libexec/s2i       com.redhat.component="s2i-core-container"       name="centos7/s2i-core-centos7"       version="1"       maintainer="SoftwareCollections.org <sclorg@redhat.com>"

/bin/sh -c #(nop) ENV     STI_SCRIPTS_URL=image:///usr/libexec/s2i     STI_SCRIPTS_PATH=/usr/libexec/s2i     APP_ROOT=/opt/app-root     HOME=/opt/app-root/src     PATH=/opt/app-root/src/bin:/opt/app-root/bin:$PATH     PLATFORM="el7"

/bin/sh -c rpmkeys --import file:///etc/pki/rpm-gpg/RPM-GPG-KEY-CentOS-7 &&   INSTALL_PKGS="bsdtar   findutils   gettext   groff-base   rsync   scl-utils   tar   unzip   yum-utils" &&   mkdir -p ${HOME}/.pki/nssdb &&   chown -R 1001:0 ${HOME}/.pki &&   yum install -y --setopt=tsflags=nodocs $INSTALL_PKGS &&   rpm -V $INSTALL_PKGS &&   yum -y clean all --enablerepo='*'
/bin/sh -c rpm-file-permissions &&   useradd -u 1001 -r -g 0 -d ${HOME} -s /sbin/nologin       -c "Default Application User" default &&   chown -R 1001:0 ${APP_ROOT}

/bin/sh -c #(nop) LABEL summary="$SUMMARY"       description="$DESCRIPTION"       io.k8s.description="$DESCRIPTION"       io.k8s.display-name="s2i core"       io.openshift.s2i.scripts-url=image:///usr/libexec/s2i       io.s2i.scripts-url=image:///usr/libexec/s2i       com.redhat.component="s2i-core-container"       name="centos7/s2i-core-centos7"       version="1"       maintainer="SoftwareCollections.org <sclorg@redhat.com>"

/bin/sh -c #(nop) ENV     STI_SCRIPTS_URL=image:///usr/libexec/s2i     STI_SCRIPTS_PATH=/usr/libexec/s2i     APP_ROOT=/opt/app-root     HOME=/opt/app-root/src     PATH=/opt/app-root/src/bin:/opt/app-root/bin:$PATH     PLATFORM="el7"

/bin/sh -c rpmkeys --import file:///etc/pki/rpm-gpg/RPM-GPG-KEY-CentOS-7 &&   INSTALL_PKGS="bsdtar   findutils   gettext   groff-base   rsync   scl-utils   tar   unzip   yum-utils" &&   mkdir -p ${HOME}/.pki/nssdb &&   chown -R 1001:0 ${HOME}/.pki &&   yum install -y --setopt=tsflags=nodocs $INSTALL_PKGS &&   rpm -V $INSTALL_PKGS &&   yum -y clean all --enablerepo='*'
/bin/sh -c rpm-file-permissions &&   useradd -u 1001 -r -g 0 -d ${HOME} -s /sbin/nologin       -c "Default Application User" default &&   chown -R 1001:0 ${APP_ROOT}
